text: Heidrun Barth (born 16 March 1961) is a German rowing cox. She competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:German female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Heilbronn Category:Coxswains (rowing)
